{"tid":1972281,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"永遠的傳奇 ! ZARD 經典 Live 片段限時免費公開","createTime":"2020-04-14T12:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T04:21:42.000Z","uid":1121,"like":83,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8fcf10a534138b1b7a593c4f6a7a0fb51f85f3f7","tid":1972281,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"有留意 90 年代日本流行音樂的朋友，相信一定聽過 ZARD 這一隊組合，當中主唱歌手坂井泉水更可以說是日本流行樂壇的傳奇，而明年是 ZARD 成立 30 周年的記念，官方除了會推出記念大碟之外，同時將 ZARD 的 17 首歌曲 MV 及 Live 表演片段限時免費公開，由 4 月 14 日 ~ 5 月 4 日期間，只要透過 ZARD 官方 Youtube 頻道就可以一同緬懷坂井泉水的風采。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/01_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F01_s.jpg&h=4dd28f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NCPH9JUFESA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNCPH9JUFESA&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=d711f560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NCPH9JUFESA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9OXNkUKmf3bUx8N9l8jM2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC9OXNkUKmf3bUx8N9l8jM2w&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=3f284db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9OXNkUKmf3bUx8N9l8jM2w</a>"},{"pid":"260821961e4650ed6f4d74ea9bf1f280a796a822","tid":1972281,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8c915ecffa0e74ea4129e6ba754cf1d12c5953","tid":1972281,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"見到ZARD個名，乜都唔駛睇住，第一時間正評咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24a53ac44517dbd99cb9d8f0cb0b72c98b3f0d7","tid":1972281,"uid":104804,"